# Endless Runner â€“ Final Assessment

## Overview
A 3D Endless Runner game developed in Unity.  
The player runs forward automatically, avoids obstacles, collects coins, and survives as long as possible while difficulty increases dynamically over time.

## Controls
- Left / Right Arrows: Change lanes
- Space / Up Arrow: Jump
- ESC: Pause / Resume
- Mouse: UI interaction

## Features
- Auto-runner player movement with lane switching
- Random obstacle spawning using prefabs
- Coin collectibles with score system
- Increasing difficulty using Scriptable Objects
- High score persistence
- Pause menu with volume control
- Game over screen with score and time survived
- Particle effects and sound effects
- Background music

## Technologies
- Unity 6
- C#
- TextMeshPro
- Scriptable Objects
- Unity UI System

## How to Play
1. Press Start from the main menu
2. Avoid obstacles and collect coins
3. Try to beat your highest score

## Build
Run the provided executable file to play the game.
